---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="SV Hochdorf 1955 – Verein">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-forest-900 to-forest-800 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-6">
        <img
          src="/img/wappen1.jpg"
          alt="Vereinswappen SV Hochdorf"
          class="w-20 h-20 sm:w-24 sm:h-24 rounded-full border-2 border-gold-500/40 object-cover shadow-lg"
        />
        <div>
          <span
            class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gold-400 border border-gold-500/30 rounded-full mb-2"
            >Verein</span
          >
          <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
            Über unseren Verein
          </h1>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-forest-100/80 max-w-2xl">
        Gegründet am 15.10.1955 in Hochdorf, steht der Schützenverein Hochdorf
        e.V. für generationsübergreifenden Schießsport, Kameradschaft und
        aktives Dorfleben.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article
        class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-sand-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-forest-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-forest-700"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M12 6.042A8.967 8.967 0 006 3.75c-1.052 0-2.062.18-3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 016 18c2.305 0 4.408.867 6 2.292m0-14.25a8.966 8.966 0 016-2.292c1.052 0 2.062.18 3 .512v14.25A8.987 8.987 0 0018 18a8.967 8.967 0 00-6 2.292m0-14.25v14.25"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-forest-900 mb-2">
          Historie & Gründung
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-forest-700/70 leading-relaxed">
          Erste Pokalwettbewerbe fanden bereits 1955 statt. Seitdem prägen
          Vereinsarbeit, Eigenleistung und sportliche Entwicklung unsere
          Geschichte.
        </p>
      </article>

      <a
        href="/chronik"
        class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-sand-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 block"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-gold-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-gold-500"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2
          class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-forest-900 mb-2 group-hover:text-gold-500 transition-colors"
        >
          Chronik
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-forest-700/70 leading-relaxed">
          Die wichtigsten Stationen von 1955 bis 2003 sind auf unserer
          Chronikseite zusammengefasst.
        </p>
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-gold-500"
        >
          Zur Chronik
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
            ><path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path></svg
          >
        </span>
      </a>

      <article
        class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md border border-sand-200 p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"
      >
        <div
          class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-forest-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 text-forest-700"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-forest-900 mb-2">
          Vorstand & Dokumente
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-forest-700/70 leading-relaxed">
          Ansprechpartner der Vorstandschaft sowie Satzung und Mitgliedsantrag
          werden fortlaufend aktualisiert.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
